# Law Hub — what NOT to commit.
#
# The served read data lives in Vercel Blob (uploaded via scripts/upload-blob.mjs).
# Local data/ stays on disk for dev (the Vite middleware reads it directly) and
# for re-ingestion runs (the scripts write here). None of it belongs in git —
# the corpus is too big and will only grow as state/municipal codes land.

data/raw/
data/build/
data/normalized/
data/index/
data/coverage/
data/geo/

node_modules/
app/node_modules/
app/.vercel/
.vercel/

.DS_Store
*.log
